        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks FG for issues of <hi rend="italic">Revue</hi> [<hi rend="italic">Scientifique</hi> vol. 7, containing lectures by Claude Bernard].</p> 
            <p>Ogle says twins [with crooked fingers] are his sisters.</p> 
<p>Recommends book by M. A. Puvis [<hi rend="italic">De la dégénération des variétés de végétaux</hi> (1837)].</p> 
